About Skinmatics

Cosmetic Dermatology Specialists in Bengaluru

Founded in 2009, Skinmatics has grown from a single clinic in Hennur to Bengaluru's most trusted name in aesthetic dermatology. We combine cutting-edge technology with deep clinical expertise and a genuine commitment to your skin's long-term health.

Our board-certified dermatologists believe in honest consultations before recommending any treatment. Because great skin starts with understanding.

Treatments we're known for

All Treatments
01 Acne & Scar Correction Chemical peels, micro-needling & laser resurfacing for lasting clarity and even texture.
02 Anti-Ageing Aesthetics Botox, fillers, threads and bio-stimulators for a naturally youthful appearance.
03 Laser Hair Reduction Diode laser technology for permanent, pain-free reduction on all Indian skin tones.
04 Pigmentation Therapy IPL, Q-switch laser and targeted chemical treatments for melasma and post-acne marks.
05 Hair Restoration PRP, GFC therapy and advanced trichology for visible, sustained hair regrowth.
